      "description": "\"I will bring you on with me into the future's light\"\n\nLately I've been watching this beautiful anime and became bewitched by its story and characters. I couldn't resist to bring these beloved characters into the physical realm.\n\nFrieren the mage\n\nI modeled these characters with a lot of love and attention to details. They are designed and scaled to be printed at 1:10 scale, but you can scale them to your liking (or to make them fit your figures collection, if you have one)\n\nI have included a personalized base for each character, featuring a motif for each character (a dungeon's stone floor for frieren, a great hall floor for Himmel, A holy pentagram seal for Heiter and Celtic design for Eisen) I chose a hexagon style in order to organize them together, and I plan to do this for the next figures I make.\n\nThese are 3D models designed for printing, textures are not included. Please leave a like and a rating if you enjoy it and post your makes!\n\nThis file is for your personal use only, and resale is prohibited.\n\nIf you like the models featured here, you can check them out, and some more, here: My creations",
      "printSettings": "These files are optimized for resin printers, but at larger scales can be printed in FDM printers. \n\nThis time I decided to use couplings for joining the pieces, and I used a tolerance of around 0.2mm to account for resin expansion, but it's always best to check your settings to avoid over exposure.\n\nThe figures come pre scaled at 1:10, and are about 14cm to 20cm in height (assembled)",
